---
---

<section class="our-story section">
  <div class="container our-story__inner">
    <div class="our-story__media reveal">
      <img src="/images/basecamp-interior.jpg" alt="Warm interior of a Rangeway driver's lounge" loading="lazy" />
      <span class="our-story__caption">Driver's Lounge · Basecamp</span>
    </div>
    <div class="our-story__text reveal">
      <p class="eyebrow">Our Story</p>
      <h2>Hospitality DNA meets EV passion.</h2>
      <p>
        Rangeway sits at the intersection of two worlds. One is a 15-year hospitality career
        across luxury resorts, wellness retreats, and flagship urban hotels, where we learned what
        a great stop feels like. The other is a deep presence in the EV driver community, leading
        clubs and hosting podcasts, where we learned what charging could be. Rangeway is what
        happens when those worlds meet.
      </p>
      <a class="btn-link" href="/our-story">
        Read our story
        <svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
          <line x1="5" y1="12" x2="19" y2="12" />
          <polyline points="13 6 19 12 13 18" />
        </svg>
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .our-story__inner {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: var(--space-8);
    align-items: center;
  }

  .our-story__media {
    position: relative;
    aspect-ratio: 4 / 5;
    overflow: hidden;
    border-radius: var(--radius-xl);
    box-shadow: var(--shadow);
  }

  .our-story__media img {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    object-fit: cover;
  }

  .our-story__caption {
    position: absolute;
    left: 18px;
    bottom: 18px;
    padding: 7px 11px;
    border-radius: var(--radius-pill);
    background: rgba(24, 21, 20, 0.7);
    color: var(--color-white);
    backdrop-filter: blur(8px);
    -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(8px);
    font-family: var(--font-heading);
    font-size: 0.72rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    font-weight: 600;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.14);
  }

  .our-story__text h2 {
    margin-bottom: var(--space-5);
    text-wrap: balance;
  }

  .our-story__text p {
    font-size: 1.08rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
    color: var(--color-text);
    max-width: 52ch;
  }

  .our-story__text .btn-link {
    margin-top: var(--space-4);
  }

  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    .our-story__inner {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
    .our-story__media {
      aspect-ratio: 16 / 10;
    }
    .our-story__caption {
      left: 12px;
      bottom: 12px;
      padding: 5px 9px;
      font-size: 0.64rem;
      letter-spacing: 0.06em;
    }
  }
</style>
